title: Guitars of the World Icons (Part One)
description:
Guitars of the World Icons (Part One):



This guitar pictures can be used as an icon for (desktop)folders or use them for making your own creation with the included high quality PNG file - Using Photoshop or any other program that your comfortable with..

Create a new folder and name it 'custom Icons'or something similar. I myself created it in the 'C:Windows'folder. That's pretty safe because you don't often use This folder so less change you delete them !! Now you can use them to make your desktop a lot more rock !!!!

To read how to change foldericons just search the Web and you get thousands of links AND it isn't hard to do at all... 

Most simple way is to right a folder and choose proportions, customize, change icon, Browse (to your new created folder and just choose an .ico file, simple as that... 

If you like this 'Part One' please leave a comment and i place a part two with a lot more within a few days..!!!!!!!!
